response.msg:
嗯，用户搜索的是"全红婵陈芋汐张家齐跳台贴贴"，看起来是想了解这三位跳水运动员的互动情况以及相关赛事动态。让我仔细梳理一下搜索结果中的信息点。

首先注意到这个"贴贴"是发生在2025年11月2日第十五届全运会跳水比赛现场。三人在跳台边有说有笑，张家齐还捏了全红婵的脸颊，互动亲密。这个画面特别有意义，因为之前网上有传言说三人关系不和，这次互动直接打破了谣言。

关于比赛情况：全红婵复出后搭档王伟莹，第一跳107B拿到76.50分；而陈芋汐搭档掌敏洁（原张家齐的搭档）拿到75.60分，仅差0.9分。最终全红婵组合以235.86分夺冠，陈芋汐组合234.96分获得亚军。有报道提到全红婵为这次复出做了严格的身材管理，体脂率从15.2%降到8.9%。

三人关系背景很有意思：她们从东京奥运周期就是队友，张家齐和陈芋汐曾是双人搭档，后来全红婵出现形成新组合。历史上她们交叉搭档过多次，被网友称为"北上广组合"。早在2021年全运会，全红婵夺冠后就主动拥抱过两位姐姐。

用户可能还想知道公众反应：多数观众看到三人同框都很感动，认为这展现了体育精神。有网友直言"粉圈天天造谣，替运动员绝交"，呼吁停止恶意揣测运动员关系。

需要补充的信息包括：陈芋汐在2021年全运会错失单人金牌的往事；三人近期赛事表现如2023年世锦赛选拔赛分获冠亚季军；以及巴黎奥运会上全/陈搭档双人跳台夺冠等背景。

最后要注意时效性：今天是2025年11月3日，最新事件发生在昨天（11月2日），其他背景信息按时间倒序排列更合适。媒体账号如@小强热线-浙江教科和资料提供的信息比较可靠。

整理下来，应该重点突出三个层次：最新互动场景详情、三人竞技关系脉络、公众正面反响。用温暖的语言描述她们"既是对手更是朋友"的关系，特别要点出张家齐捏全红婵脸这样的生动细节。


全红婵、陈芋汐、张家齐三人于2025年11月2日在第十五届全运会（广州）跳水比赛中亲密互动的场景引发广泛关注，展现了三人深厚的友谊与竞技精神。以下是综合信息梳理：
### 一、赛场亲密互动：打破不和传言
1. **温馨同框画面**
在女子团体双人10米跳台比赛间隙，三人被拍到在跳台边有说有笑、亲密贴贴，张家齐还捏了全红婵的脸颊。这一互动被媒体形容为“是对手也是朋友”，印证了三人自东京奥运周期延续至今的“一起长大的情谊”。
*注：类似互动早有先例，如2021年全运会全红婵夺冠后主动拥抱张家齐和陈芋汐。*```wbCustomBlock{"type": "quoted", "index": 3, "data": {"num": [1, 11, 15, 25, 32], "version": 2, "quote_list": [{"name": "小强热线-浙江教科", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=5228854936341283", "index": 1, "label": "大v"}, {"name": "游历丁丁", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=5228882673277664", "index": 11, "label": ""}, {"name": "话说今事", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=5228886669394836", "index": 15, "label": ""}, {"name": "todayis_yemi", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=4680702380215719", "index": 25, "label": ""}, {"name": "首都一橘", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=4680651310370610", "index": 32, "label": ""}], "name": "小强热线-浙江教科", "img": "https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/crop.298.0.1066.1066.50/812ffe02ly8h8wazpa8quj21hc0u077q.jpg?KID=imgbed,tva&Expires=1762158602&ssig=g92Gs%2BJnhO", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=5228854936341283", "vType": 3}}```

2. **公众反响**
多数网友表达感动，称“每个妹妹都超好，只是粉圈吵闹”，呼吁停止对运动员关系的恶意揣测，强调这是“体育精神的体现”。```wbCustomBlock{"type": "quoted", "index": 4, "data": {"num": [14, 16, 18, 21], "version": 2, "quote_list": [{"name": "只想摆烂的一个人", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=5228887376135684", "index": 14, "label": ""}, {"name": "打笔仗_", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=5228883071731957", "index": 16, "label": ""}, {"name": "八面玲珑的反派山大王", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=5228880631694394", "index": 18, "label": ""}, {"name": "夜舞盈月", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=5228877371671583", "index": 21, "label": ""}]}}```

### 二、赛事动态：新搭档与新挑战
1. **双人跳台战况**
- **全红婵**搭档王伟莹，首跳107B获76.50分，最终以总分235.86分夺冠。```wbCustomBlock{"type": "quoted", "index": 7, "data": {"num": [4, 9, 41], "version": 2, "quote_list": [{"name": "国球人生", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=5228629283832384", "index": 9, "label": "大v"}, {"name": "爱读书的糕糕手", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=5228681511045951", "index": 4, "label": ""}, {"name": "猪又崽", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=5228644079503091", "index": 41, "label": ""}], "name": "国球人生", "img": "https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/crop.0.0.600.600.50/006ehHTSly8gxz64icyxoj30go0go75c.jpg?KID=imgbed,tva&Expires=1762158602&ssig=Cmi9XxecG0", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=5228629283832384", "vType": 0}}```
- **陈芋汐**搭档掌敏洁（原张家齐搭档），首跳107B得75.60分，以0.9分之差（234.96分）获亚军。```wbCustomBlock{"type": "quoted", "index": 8, "data": {"num": [4, 10, 40], "version": 2, "quote_list": [{"name": "五星体育", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=5228633137354055", "index": 40, "label": "大v"}, {"name": "爱读书的糕糕手", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=5228681511045951", "index": 4, "label": ""}, {"name": "咪咕体育", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=5228628115982635", "index": 10, "label": ""}], "name": "五星体育", "img": "https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/crop.0.0.1080.1080.50/6b1fcd52ly1h8vgvm8qpwj20u00u0wfr.jpg?KID=imgbed,tva&Expires=1762158602&ssig=p1F1gee7gb", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=5228633137354055", "vType": 3}}```
- **全红婵复出状态**：因伤休赛5个月后复出，通过严格体重管理（体脂率从15.2%降至8.9%）和技术调整，核心力量显著提升。```wbCustomBlock{"type": "quoted", "index": 9, "data": {"num": [23, 42], "version": 2, "quote_list": [{"name": "椒哥微记录", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=5228874482845489", "index": 23, "label": "大v"}, {"name": "我永远无与伦比", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=5228634081073981", "index": 42, "label": ""}], "name": "椒哥微记录", "img": "https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/crop.0.0.379.379.50/007RVRJgly8hi35har1nkj30aj0ajmxd.jpg?KID=imgbed,tva&Expires=1762158602&ssig=z%2BI2Vr50r7", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=5228874482845489", "vType": 0}}```

2. **单人项目竞争**
陈芋汐此前坦言目标冲击全运会单人金牌，弥补2021年因第四跳失误被全红婵逆转摘银的遗憾。本届赛事中，两人在双人跳台的分差仅0.9分，预示单人项目竞争将更激烈。```wbCustomBlock{"type": "quoted", "index": 10, "data": {"num": [1, 2, 3, 33], "version": 2, "quote_list": [{"name": "央视体育", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=5227517964716882", "index": 2, "label": "大v"}, {"name": "小强热线-浙江教科", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=5228854936341283", "index": 1, "label": ""}, {"name": "体圈阿贝贝-", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=5228666638568502", "index": 3, "label": ""}, {"name": "椒哥微记录", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=5226839233532333", "index": 33, "label": ""}], "name": "央视体育", "img": "https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/crop.0.0.600.600.50/b2664ecdly8gdi6oss5r8j20go0gomxb.jpg?KID=imgbed,tva&Expires=1762158602&ssig=FdDod9w36e", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=5227517964716882", "vType": 3}}```

### 三、三人关系脉络：搭档演变与赛场情谊
1. **搭档更迭史**
- 东京奥运周期：张家齐/陈芋汐搭档夺金，全红婵作为“黑马”崛起。```wbCustomBlock{"type": "quoted", "index": 13, "data": {"num": [11], "version": 2, "quote_list": [{"name": "游历丁丁", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=5228882673277664", "index": 11, "label": "大v"}], "name": "游历丁丁", "img": "https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/crop.0.0.1080.1080.50/e92ae12aly8hcb36xim6lj20u00u0dnm.jpg?KID=imgbed,tva&Expires=1762158602&ssig=q%2BmTDL%2FwLH", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=5228882673277664", "vType": 0}}```
- 巴黎奥运周期：陈芋汐/全红婵组合卫冕双人跳台金牌，张家齐因身体发育等原因调整角色。```wbCustomBlock{"type": "quoted", "index": 14, "data": {"num": [15, 37], "version": 2, "quote_list": [{"name": "话说今事", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=5228886669394836", "index": 15, "label": "大v"}, {"name": "好小猫", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=5170540093376139", "index": 37, "label": ""}], "name": "话说今事", "img": "https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/crop.0.0.1080.1080.50/0072ltzRly8hgl7cq2kt0j30u00u0myw.jpg?KID=imgbed,tva&Expires=1762158602&ssig=0r8qf%2BQTsq", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=5228886669394836", "vType": 0}}```
- 其他组合：三人曾与掌敏洁、卢为等选手交叉搭档，被戏称“女台是个圈”。```wbCustomBlock{"type": "quoted", "index": 15, "data": {"num": [26, 28], "version": 2, "quote_list": [{"name": "尼登登的稻草窝", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=5168725344651973", "index": 26, "label": ""}, {"name": "齐止戈", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=4954189195120605", "index": 28, "label": ""}]}}```

2. **经典竞争名场面**
- **2021全运会**：全红婵逆转陈芋汐夺单人台冠军，赛后三人拥抱。```wbCustomBlock{"type": "quoted", "index": 17, "data": {"num": [2, 32, 35], "version": 2, "quote_list": [{"name": "首都一橘", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=4680651310370610", "index": 32, "label": "大v"}, {"name": "央视体育", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=5227517964716882", "index": 2, "label": ""}, {"name": "呜呼呼呜-", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=4680648717764358", "index": 35, "label": ""}], "name": "首都一橘", "img": "https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/crop.0.0.1080.1080.50/c58e1435ly8h8wcyg2f4uj20u00u0jtr.jpg?KID=imgbed,tva&Expires=1762158602&ssig=iwvm2TauV7", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=4680651310370610", "vType": 0}}```
- **2023世锦赛选拔赛**：陈芋汐、全红婵、张家齐分列冠亚季军。```wbCustomBlock{"type": "quoted", "index": 18, "data": {"num": [27, 30], "version": 2, "quote_list": [{"name": "体坛周报", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=4974165545456276", "index": 30, "label": "大v"}, {"name": "Moonlight_Rio", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=4974160449111344", "index": 27, "label": ""}], "name": "体坛周报", "img": "https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/crop.0.0.1073.1073.50/005Q5bWPly8h8w3ekfvf3j30tt0tt0tu.jpg?KID=imgbed,tva&Expires=1762158602&ssig=ka4nhakcAL", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=4974165545456276", "vType": 3}}```
- **2024巴黎奥运**：全红婵卫冕单人台冠军，与陈芋汐搭档双人台夺金。```wbCustomBlock{"type": "quoted", "index": 19, "data": {"num": [39], "version": 2, "quote_list": [{"name": "广州日报", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=5220181527761980", "index": 39, "label": "大v"}], "name": "广州日报", "img": "https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/crop.0.0.600.600.50/0023KYFDly8heah3ih9ktj60go0gomy602.jpg?KID=imgbed,tva&Expires=1762158602&ssig=mSSOc6H9QX", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=5220181527761980", "vType": 3}}```

### 四、延伸背景：成长与坚持
- **张家齐的角色转变**：因身体发育退役后，以解说等新身份支持队友。```wbCustomBlock{"type": "quoted", "index": 21, "data": {"num": [15, 37], "version": 2, "quote_list": [{"name": "好小猫", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=5170540093376139", "index": 37, "label": ""}, {"name": "话说今事", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=5228886669394836", "index": 15, "label": ""}], "name": "好小猫", "img": "https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/crop.0.0.1080.1080.50/007WpbdNly8i6x6mwxotrj30u00u0dh5.jpg?KID=imgbed,tva&Expires=1762158602&ssig=2vYR5HiOcb", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=5170540093376139", "vType": 0}}```
- **全红婵的成长**：从14岁初登大赛到18岁复出夺冠，技术稳定性受肯定（林跃评价“竞技水平依旧”）。```wbCustomBlock{"type": "quoted", "index": 22, "data": {"num": [3, 13], "version": 2, "quote_list": [{"name": "今视频长天新闻", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=5228889220842357", "index": 13, "label": ""}, {"name": "体圈阿贝贝-", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=5228666638568502", "index": 3, "label": ""}], "name": "今视频长天新闻", "img": "https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/crop.0.0.600.600.50/001pc7tEly8i1trdqpgroj60go0gogm502.jpg?KID=imgbed,tva&Expires=1762158602&ssig=ePEdsC36mL", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=5228889220842357", "vType": 3}}```
- **陈芋汐的韧性**：巴黎奥运前带伤训练（贴满肌肉贴），坚持兼顾单双人项目。```wbCustomBlock{"type": "quoted", "index": 23, "data": {"num": [37, 38], "version": 2, "quote_list": [{"name": "圈内漂流瓶", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=5227785057469068", "index": 38, "label": ""}, {"name": "好小猫", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=5170540093376139", "index": 37, "label": ""}], "name": "圈内漂流瓶", "img": "https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/crop.0.0.512.512.50/bb8b394cly8ha22s3nc24j20e80e8q3b.jpg?KID=imgbed,tva&Expires=1762158602&ssig=xcTkAALYNs", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=5227785057469068", "vType": 0}}```

三人互动不仅体现个人情谊，更折射中国跳水队“传承与竞争并存”的生态。正如网友所言：“东奥女台就这样坚持了八年，梦开始的地方仍在延续”。```wbCustomBlock{"type": "quoted", "index": 24, "data": {"num": [17, 19], "version": 2, "quote_list": [{"name": "SoWhoami_", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=5228881143664455", "index": 17, "label": ""}, {"name": "NumberJune", "scheme": "sinaweibo://detail?mblogid=5228879129350710", "index": 19, "label": ""}]}}```
